04:32.440 --> 04:33.440
Yeah, yeah, I understand.

04:33.440 --> 04:37.440
I mean, I think that when,

04:37.440 --> 04:40.440
here's what I think we mean when we say we created a computer.

04:40.440 --> 04:45.440
