05:06.440 --> 05:12.440
But so I'm sort of shifting the focus on the observer

05:12.440 --> 05:17.440
and the interpretation of various events by an observer.

05:17.440 --> 05:19.440
So somebody else can see the same events and interpret them

05:19.440 --> 05:21.440
